> [4] http://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=97426#c8
> [5] https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=748379
> 
> Could you allocate a CVE id for this? (as it looks there isn't one
> for this deficiency yet)
